  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个数据包调度器的整体架构。核心是从APB接口进来的描述符处理，然后到调度器做读写控制。你先帮我搭个框架，把APB Interface和Configuration这两个输入源放在顶层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB",
        "CFG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，APB Interface带apb_valid和addr信号，Configuration是独立配置源。这两个都连到Descriptor Engine对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB",
        "CFG",
        "DESC_ENG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，DESC_ENG是描述符引擎的核心。它要通过AXI去读描述符内存，你加上DESC_AXI这个模块，用desc_ar_*信号组连过去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC_ENG",
        "DESC_AXI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加DESC_AXI，标注了AXI AR/R通道。那读回来的数据怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC_AXI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "读回来的desc_r_data送到DESC_PARSE做解析，解析完的256-bit descriptor_packet输出到DESC_OUT。这是描述符流水线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC_AXI",
        "DESC_PARSE",
        "DESC_OUT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "描述符链路完成了。DESC_OUT用descriptor_valid/ready握手连到后面的调度器？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC_OUT",
        "SCHED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，SCHED是Scheduler FSM，收到描述符后发起数据读写。它要输出datard_valid/addr/beats给读接口，还有对应的写控制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHED",
        "RD_IF",
        "WR_IF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加了RD_IF和WR_IF。这两个接口是调度器的执行臂，分别处理数据读和数据写。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RD_IF",
        "WR_IF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "RD_IF和WR_IF要连到真正的AXI引擎，你加上RD_ENG和WR_ENG。另外，读写完成要有反馈，RD_ENG回datard_done给RD_IF，WR_ENG回datawr_done给WR_IF。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RD_IF",
        "WR_IF",
        "RD_ENG",
        "WR_ENG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
