      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有两路监控。DESC_ENG要输出mon_valid/packet到DESC_MON，Agent ID是0x10；SCHED要输出到SCHED_MON，Agent ID是0x30。",
